"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1934260-Daniel-Wiffen-Olympics-Ireland\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Daniel Wiffen has revealed that his final few days at theOlympicswill be filled with partying after delivering one gold and one bronze medal for Ireland in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9979677787480634, \"rank\": 0.002036159812665469, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 158, \"end\": 163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999932119863, \"rank\": 6.787995166025813e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old has been one of the revelations of the 2024 Olympics swimming programme, storming to a gold medal in the 800m freestyle before settling for bronze in a blockbuster 1500m freestyle final in which Team USA's Bobby Finke shattered the world record.\", \"from\": 166, \"to\": 427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 377, \"end\": 385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9646496747313569, \"rank\": 0.036549715252042994, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 388, \"end\": 399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bobby Finke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ireland's swimming sensation then swapped the aquatics centre for the River Seine, taking part in the men's marathon swim, which involved six laps of a 1.6-kilometre loop, totalling 10km of action through the heart of Paris.\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 429, \"end\": 436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9979677787480634, \"rank\": 0.002036159812665469, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 499, \"end\": 510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 647, \"end\": 652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999932119863, \"rank\": 6.787995166025813e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The marathon swim was something of a bonus event for Wiffen, who struggled to hold pace with the leading pack during the early stages of the race.\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the Irish star dug deep and eventually crossed the line in 18th place, bringing a respectable end to an exceptional Olympic campaign.\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 944, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 815, \"end\": 820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9364178668969514, \"rank\": 0.054748163271184425, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked how he'd be capping off his time in Paris, Wiffen said: \\\"So it'll probably be party time tonight, party time Saturday, closing ceremony, then party time again.\\\"\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 1112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999932119863, \"rank\": 6.787995166025813e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1218, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1249, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Wiffen is seemingly in no rush to return to open-water swimming.\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Leeds-born athlete was taken aback by the difficulty of the marathon swim event.\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the pool, it is easy when there are eight people in a final, and there are about 30 people in it here,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was about two minutes down from the front of the pack.\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1604, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was like 'Do I really want to finish?\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"', but I needed to finish it and I am glad to say I am an Olympic open water swimmer.\\\"\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1730, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"A lot of people would say it's the worst race they have ever done, in terms of the currents.\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1834, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So for my first one to be the hardest and I came 18th, I am very happy.\\\"\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1907, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 2018, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2095, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2128, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Wiffen used the opportunity to put his name into the hat to carry the Irish flag at the closing ceremony.\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2223, \"end\": 2233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Irish flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am Olympic champion, Olympic bronze medallist and placed 18th in the open water,\\\" he stated.\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2354, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could not have asked for anything more.\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am the only double medallist [for Team Ireland], so it's kind of cool.\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2435, \"end\": 2447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999976873823, \"rank\": 2.3123690878525897e-09, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will maybe put it out there that I am hopefully carrying the flag.\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2540, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We do not know yet but that's what I want.\\\"\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2723, \"end\": 2736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.684093217567519e-16, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2772, \"end\": 2785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.684093217567519e-16, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"